Using an animal picture instead of their own on a dating site or social media account could mean a few different things. It's possible that the person is trying to protect their privacy by not using their own photo. They might also be trying to be humorous or stand out from the crowd. However  it's important to remember that using an animal picture could also be a red flag for potential dishonesty or lack of transparency. When engaging with someone using an animal picture  it's a good idea to approach with caution and verify their identity before forming any serious connections.
